{"tid":1007770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共軍賀歲恐嚇片《戰鷹繞寶島飛》中国網友：完成統一大業","createTime":"2019-02-04T04:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T00:53:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1c18d0ca36d228ced70064d597e782a103bafc30","tid":1007770,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpcN6XV0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpcN6XV0.jpg&h=fdcc231e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人民解放軍今（3日）以「賀歲首發」為註記，上傳一首新歌《我的戰鷹繞著寶島飛》，歌詞提到「我的戰鷹繞著寶島飛／捎來故鄉的思念輕聲喚你歸」、「聽阿里山的姑娘不斷回味／她的溫柔恰似日月潭水」，MV中除了放入中共戰機等畫面，還讓台北101大樓與中共空降兵徽同框，挑釁意味濃厚。<br />\n<br />\n中共空降兵部隊官方微信帳號「我們的天空（ID碼：OurSky-kj）」今（3日）上傳新歌《我的戰鷹繞著寶島飛》MV，許多中國網友回應，「太好聽了」、「加油，早日完成國家統一大業」。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部新聞發言人大校吳謙日前曾揚言，台灣若「以武拒統只有死路一條」；空軍新聞發言人大校申進科說過，將按既定計畫繼續組織多型戰機繞飛台島巡航，並且有「堅定的意志、充分的信心和足夠的能力」，「捍衛國家主權和領土完整」。<br />\n<br />\nPTT網友回應，「跟噁男差不多，偶爾到女生家樓下唱歌、放話等等」、「使用101當背景前要先取得授權吧」、「這跟韓國瑜的mv差不多感覺」、「呱吉溜滑板的youtube影片片段也被剪進去了」、「反正這也不是在youtube在支媒（中國媒體），所以也不用檢舉啥智財（智慧財產權）了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php05mlHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php05mlHo.jpg&h=ced75df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《我的戰鷹繞著寶島飛》歌詞：<br />\n<br />\n讀余光中的鄉愁我曾流淚<br />\n<br />\n那一彎海峽隔不斷山水<br />\n<br />\n請海鷗轉告我的兄弟姐妹<br />\n<br />\n十五的明月才更圓更美<br />\n<br />\n我的戰鷹繞著寶島飛<br />\n<br />\n捎來故鄉的思念輕聲喚你歸<br />\n<br />\n我的戰鷹繞著寶島飛<br />\n<br />\n繞著寶島飛<br />\n<br />\n把每朵親愛的雲塞進我心扉<br />\n<br />\n聽阿里山的姑娘不斷回味<br />\n<br />\n她的溫柔恰似日月潭水<br />\n<br />\n太平洋的風吹拂我銀頭盔<br />\n<br />\n未曾飲一杯我心已沉醉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2691765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2691765&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=e785bcbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2691765&h=e5376e5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2691765</a>"},{"pid":"465449123a08c4bc81033ed8d269bb0e4e99d4e1","tid":1007770,"uid":205462,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a02zVJz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa02zVJz.jpg&h=65ac678a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4820ac3677820c6456ccb78a173105749726a37","tid":1007770,"uid":6752,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.kekeke.cc/t/ObMkNjr8IX.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.kekeke.cc%2Ft%2FObMkNjr8IX.jpeg&h=12536456&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2254816da89df3966be96cf61719bc27fbcb09e5","tid":1007770,"uid":18127,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9479559f3833970f05ee25224646a6c70ac00b82","tid":1007770,"uid":1372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:31:30.000Z","msg":"有無呱吉果段睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c009fcd817397cea8b38381aa7232051a193b1","tid":1007770,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bea23c2a72211767786b44e3d2fbcf991f06892","tid":1007770,"uid":6030,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ruq4nW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3